---
// Testimonials.astro
---
<section class="py-24 bg-gray-50 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-secondary sm:text-4xl">What our UK clients say</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Join over 10,000 happy customers across the United Kingdom.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 relative">
        <div class="flex text-yellow-400 mb-4 text-xl">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 italic">"I switched from Premium Cable because it was too expensive. The picture quality here is exactly the same, and the buffer-free sports channels are a lifesaver on match days."</p>
        <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-primary font-bold">SM</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-secondary text-sm">Steven M.</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">London, UK</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 relative">
        <div class="flex text-yellow-400 mb-4 text-xl">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 italic">"The setup was incredibly easy. I use it on my Firestick, and the VOD section is huge. Better than Major VOD Platforms and Prime combined for a fraction of the cost."</p>
        <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-primary font-bold">EJ</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-secondary text-sm">Emma J.</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">Manchester, UK</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 relative">
        <div class="flex text-yellow-400 mb-4 text-xl">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 italic">"Fantastic customer support. I had a minor issue setting up Tivimate and they walked me through it on WhatsApp in 5 minutes. Highly recommended!"</p>
        <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-primary font-bold">DT</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-secondary text-sm">David T.</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">Birmingham, UK</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
